snippet.title: Nabodurga - Bangla Durga Puja Songs | Bengali Songs - Mahalaya - Mahishasura Mardini

localized.description:
Enjoy these most popular Bangla Non Stop Devotional Songs & Stay connected with us:-

✿ Subscribe us for more Bengali videos : http://goo.gl/9M4tiF

✿ Like us on Facebook :
http://www.facebook.com/unisysmovies

Presenting the top Bangla Non Stop songs for Navratri 2014 from "Nabodurga" album duet by Nirmalya Roy & Modhurima Datta Chowdhury. The music of the songs are directed by Bickram Ghosh and lyrics are given by Krishnalal Mukherjee. Enjoy these Bengali Durga Puja Songs

Listen, Like & share !!!

Songs Included in this jukebox are :

1. Aji Anondo - 00:01
2. Borisho Dharar Majhe - 02:06
3. Durge Durge -  05:13
4. Jayo Jayo Durga - 14:35
5. Kato Roop - 17:23
6. Lilamoyee Maa - 22:20
7. Nama Namo Mata - 29:59
8. Santi Dayini - 31:41

Album Credentials :

Album : Nabodurga
Singer : Nirmalya Roy & Modhurima Datta Chowdhury
Music : Bickram Ghosh
Lyricist : Krishnalal Mukherjee
Label : Indya Records
Digital Partner : Unisys


Mahalaya, signifies the termination of Pitri Paksha and the beginning of Devi Paksha, thus ushering in the season of religious festivals. It is said that Devi Durga begins her journey from her husband's abode in Kailash to her paternal home on this day. The glory of Durga is known from the ancient treatise Durga Saptasati or the Chandi
